# Web UI (webui.py)

- Monolithic file — add `_private_helpers` near the handlers that use them.
- API responses use `_json_response`; streaming events use `_stream_json_event`.
- Auth/CSRF: follow existing protected POST handler patterns; never skip CSRF on authenticated writes.
- Extend `tests/test_webui_api.py` for every new or changed API route.
- Keep inline HTML/CSS/JS in-file unless explicitly asked to split modules.
